Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.21,0:22:57.18,ED歌词 日语,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\kf36\blur2}若{\kf38}草{\kf17}が{\kf39}揺{\kf23}れ{\kf36}る{\kf20}野{\kf48}へ
